Why bother calling @ConEd  to report a  power   outage ?

@ConEd  creates a
ticket based on 1st call for an area. They add other calls to that ticket. They sometimes add what is a separate issue to an existing ticket so when 1st ticket is resolved they mark all as fixed. Always call!

